<L>__{interior brandon's office day}
<A>__{a football betting form fills frame. two columns of teams seen. point spreads penciled in between them. 11 of 12 games checked off. monday night the last to be decided. pull back to show brandon in his office, the unfinished form before him. a young salesman appears at the door.}
